<noinclude>
== Unit New Template ==

This template renders an infobox for unit/chassis pages. It automatically loads data from [[Module:Chassis_data]] based on the page name.

=== Automatic Data Loading ===

When used as <code><nowiki>{{Unit New}}</nowiki></code>, the template automatically queries [[Module:Chassis_data]] using <code><nowiki>{{PAGENAME}}</nowiki></code> as the lookup key.

=== Manual Override (Backward Compatible) ===

All parameters can be manually specified to override the automatic data:

<pre>
{{Unit New
  | title1 = Example
  | image1 = Example.jpg
  | unit_type = Example
  | faction = Example
  | chassis_type = Example
  | chassis_cost = Example
  | technology_required = Example
  | other_requirements = Example
  | weapon_slots = Example
  | module_slots = Example
  | shield_slots = Example
  | reactor_slots = Example
  | weapon_tech = Example
  | shield_tech = Example
  | module_tech = Example
  | reactor_tech = Example
  | payload = Example
  | armor = Example
  | speed = Example
  | critical_hit_chance = Example
  | accuracy_adjusted = Example
  | damage_adjusted = Example
  | defensive_merit = Example
  | shield_projection = Example
  | module_uplink = Example
  | energy_distribution_/_energy_share = Example
  | energy_induction = Example
  | damage_boost = Example
  | drain_boost = Example
}}
</pre>

